1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:09,352
US forces carried out fresh strikes on Iran after a Panama-flagged tanker was hit by an alleged Iranian drone near the Strait of Hormuz.

2
00:00:09,302 --> 00:00:15,511
The incident deepened fears for commercial shipping in one of the world's most important energy routes.

3
00:00:15,511 --> 00:00:22,645
Any longer disruption could raise insurance costs, delay cargoes and increase pressure on oil markets.

